# PLANRAUM frontend environment — all optional. The app runs without any of these.
#
# Extraction goes to the Vercel serverless function at /api/extract (same-origin),
# so the frontend needs NO API URL and NO API key. The OpenAI key lives only in
# the ROOT .env (server-side) — never here, never with a VITE_ prefix.

# Cesium ion token — ONLY needed if you swap the MapLibre viewer for the
# optional CesiumJS globe (see src/viewer/). MapLibre needs no key at all.
# VITE_CESIUM_TOKEN=
